description:
Zeke is an all around athlete but mostly concentrated on football and wresting.
A friend of his had come down and done photos, but not video, and Zeke didnt have too many reservations about doing both.
Zeke is one shy guy and it's totally endearing. He is totally aware of his 'Shy Factor' and is seeking to push his limits. He gets nervous and flustered easily by the ladies, and is determined to not let life pass him by.
His body is awesome too. Thick and meaty, and I think he looks great in his ball cap. And those quads! Wow!
I hope to get Zeke back for more, so stay tuned!
title: Zeke - Solo
